Shi i amo , nankyo netu Yehova uketuyuka biyampe .
Lwa na milangwe mibi na kutweja mu ñeni yobe “ bintu byonso bya bine shi bika shi bika , byonso bilēmekwa shi bika shi bika , byonso byoloke shi bika shi bika , byonso byampikwa disubi shi bika shi bika , byonso bya kusanshibwa shi bika shi bika , byonso binenenwa biyampe shi bika shi bika , byonso bya mwikadilo muyampe shi bika shi bika , ne byonso bya kutendelwa shi bika shi bika . ” ​ — Fidipai 4 : 8 .
Batwe bantu tudi na ñeni .
Mwanda waka wielelanga’ko kwingidila Yehova na mutyima obe onso , ne muya obe onso , ne manwa obe onso , ne bukomo bobe bonso ?
( Isaya 43 : 23 ) Inoko , byakwela byādi byelwa pampikwa kusaka ne kwakubulwa buswe kebyādipo na mvubu ku meso a Yehova .
Mwanda meso andi a lwitabijo ādi amwene kintu kya bukomo kutabuka dijiba ne kibumbo kya bulwi .
( Tanga Bahebelu 13 : 2 . )
Yesu webepangula’mba : “ Le aye mwine mumubīkile pi ? ”
